Program: Discovery
Title: Fire - the firefighters
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrygc
Last Broadcast Date: 23 July 2003
A report on the firefighters who battle blazes from within. The programme looks at the work of smokejumpers, the wildland firefighters that parachute into a remote area to combat wildfires. This programme joins the smoke jumpers of the United States Forest Service in Missoula.